  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Modifications of cell surface markers (including EMMPRIN) were observed in conjunctival
      epithelial cells during dry eye syndrome ; this study aims to describe the modifications of
      the repartition of these cell surface markers before and after initiation of a treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
