  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>comparison of surface area of cell markers measured on conjunctival epithelial cells, in persons with and without severe eye dryness.</measure>
    <time_frame>baseline</time_frame>
    <description>Comparison of the mean surface in patients before treatment for eye dryness versus in persons with no eye dryness. Immunofluorescence analysed in confocal microscopy on conjunctival impression cytology.</description>
